HEADWORD: Energetics
<hw>En`er*get"ics</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That branch of
science which treats of the laws governing the physical or mechanical,
in distinction from the vital, forces, and which comprehends the
consideration and general investigation of the whole range of the forces
concerned in physical phenomena.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark></p>

